snippet.title: Stampede Racing Royale - Game Reveal Trailer | PC Gaming Show 2023
snippet.description:
Stampede Racing Royale combines a cart racer like Mario Kart with a fast-paced battle royale elimination-style game like Fall Guys. 60 drivers all compete in the same race, with 20 being eliminated each round. Collect power-ups like mines, shields, and speed boosts as you try to become the last player driving. Read more at PC Gamer: https://www.pcgamer.com/stampede-racing-royale-reveal-trailer-pcgs-2023
